#
# 0001 version --help
#
ngsi version --help

```
NAME:
   ngsi version - print the version

USAGE:
   ngsi version [command options] [arguments...]

CATEGORY:
   CONVENIENCE

OPTIONS:
   --host value, -h value  host or alias
   --token value           oauth token
   --pretty, -P            pretty format (default: false)
   --help                  show help (default: false)
   
```

